descriptionNullable:
### Context

The goal of this dataset is to provide quality images for face mask detection ml projects.


### Content

The dataset contains 180 + images under mask and no mask directories.


### Acknowledgements

The data was scraped from unsplash.com and images from several search engines.

### Inspiration

I would like for people to use this dataset to create mask detection models using Convnets.

subtitle: FaceMask dataset for ML projects
